body:
Phandom get a grip….

Phil has been in the hospital. We don’t know the cause. We can only hope he’s doing all right now.

While it’s indeed moving that Dan is there with him in whatever capacity, let’s keep Phangirling at back of our minds and wish Phil a speedy recovery.

I am a bit disheartened that fanfic prompts and naughty jokes, etc is being circulated with this event. Yeah we ship the boys till kingdom comes, but now ain’t the time . Get a grip okay. While it’s very tempting and all, don’t use it for Phan proof.
